description:
My place is close to Alantic Aveune.Few blocks away from the A and J trains. . You’ll love my place because of the new renovations, the neighborhood is quiet, Relaxing getaway , the coziness. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers.

This space is brand new I haven't fully moved in just yet.

This is a 3 bedroom with two bathroom apartment. You'll have 2 rooms out of 3 and 1 bathroom out of two completly half of the apartment. Kitchen is huge living space is decent

I will be around to help you during your stay.

A little nice walk to public transportation. Parking is not bad in front of the building
name: 2 Bedroom with 1 bathroon in Brooklyn
